'''Linux游戏'''是在[[Linux|Linux]]下运行的游戏。[[GNU/Linux|GNU/Linux]]是[[自由软件|自由软件]]，也是以[[自由软件|自由]][[开源|开源]]为旗帜。常用软件，甚至游戏类也多是[[开源软件|开源]][[免费软件|免费]]游戏。

== 歷史 ==
=== 1990年代 ===
<!-- 注释出：[[File:Doom1-ultimate.JPG|thumb]]》是最早在Linux發行的主流商業遊戲之一。]] -->

Linux遊戲的歷史開始於既有的[[Unix|Unix]]遊戲，這兩大作業系統有不少類似的遊戲。這些遊戲通常是原創或{{link-en|電子遊戲複製|Video game clone|複製版}}的[[街機遊戲|街機類遊戲]]或文字冒險遊戲。一個著名的例子是所謂的「[[BSD|BSD]]遊戲集」（BSD Games），即是一系列[[文字冒險遊戲|互動小說]]遊戲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/4169|title=Ghost of Fun Time's Past|publisher={{tsl|en|Linux Journal|}}|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2011-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607182135/http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/4169|dead-url=no}}</ref> 影響Linux開發甚大的[[自由軟體|自由軟體]]和[[開源|開源]]作法也影響了最早的免費遊戲。早期著名的遊戲包含''[[NetHack|NetHack]]、[[Netrek|Netrek]]、{{tsl|en|XBill|}}、[[XEvil|XEvil]]、[[xbattle|xbattle]]、{{tsl|en|Xconq|}}''和''{{tsl|en|XPilot|}}''。隨著Linux系統的成長，自由開源的遊戲也隨著增加，並變得更加複雜。

一般認為Linux商業電子遊戲的起源是1994年由{{link-en|戴夫·泰勒 (遊戲開發者)|Dave Taylor (game programmer)|戴夫·泰勒}}移植的《[[毀滅戰士_(1993年遊戲)|毀滅戰士]]》，他在閒暇時把這套遊戲移植到包含Linux在內的多個系統上。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/1 | title = DOOM | publisher = Linux Journal | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103044/https://www.linuxjournal.com/article/1 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/3180|title=Getting Started with Quake|publisher={{tsl|en|Linux Journal|}}|date=January 1, 1999|last=Zimbinski|first=Bob|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023121851/https://www.linuxjournal.com/article/3180|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也協助建立了 ''{{tsl|en|Crack dot Com|}}''工作室，這個工作室發行了[[Abuse_(遊戲)|Abuse]]。Linux版的Abuse甚至由[[Red_Hat|Red Hat]]公司發行。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Partnership with Crack dot Com Brings Games to Linux |url=http://www.redhat.com/about/news/press-archive/1997/10/press-crackdotcom |publisher=[[Red_Hat|Red Hat]] |date=1997-10-07 |accessdate=2014-07-31 |archive-date=2014-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808060356/http://www.redhat.com/about/news/press-archive/1997/10/press-crackdotcom |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.loonygames.com/content/1.10/guest/|title=So Long, Crack.com|publisher=loonygames|accessdate=2011-08-04|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021165111/http://www.loonygames.com/content/1.10/guest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《毀滅戰士》的開發者[[id_Software|id Software]]也在之後繼續發行遊戲到Linux上。1996年，戴夫·泰勒再次於閒暇時把[[雷神之锤_(游戏)|雷神之鎚]]移植到Linux上。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.blankmaninc.com/david-taylor-interview | title='Dave Taylor Interview - game developer' | publisher=blankmaninc.com | date=2012-10-27 | access-date=2016-02-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723204846/http://www.blankmaninc.com/david-taylor-interview/ | archive-date=2014-07-23 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://linux.omnipotent.net/article.php?article_id=11261|title=How To Install Quake 1|publisher=Linux.com|date=November 15, 2000|last=Mrochuk|first=Jeff|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803060426/http://linux.omnipotent.net/article.php?article_id=11261|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後的id遊戲由{{tsl|en|David Kirsch|}}以及{{tsl|en|Timothee Besset|}}製作Linux版，一直到id工作室2009年被[[ZeniMax_Media|ZeniMax Media]]收購才停止。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/121945-John-Carmack-Argues-Against-Native-Linux-Games|title=John Carmack Argues Against Native Linux Games|first=Andy|last=Chalk|date=2013-02-06|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2014-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113172607/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/121945-John-Carmack-Argues-Against-Native-Linux-Games|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在1995年，DUX軟體僱用Don Hopkins移植 《[[模擬城市_(1989年遊戲)|模擬城市]]》到Linux上。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.donhopkins.com/drupal/|title=History and Future of OLPC SimCity / Micropolis|access-date=2016-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113113239/http://www.donhopkins.com/drupal/|archive-date=2016-01-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>其他早期的商業Linux遊戲包含''{{tsl|en|Hopkins FBI|}}''，這是一款[[MP_Entertainment|MP Entertainment]]在1996年發行的冒險遊戲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://linux.omnipotent.net/article.php?article_id=6937|title=Hopkins FBI]|publisher=Linux.com|date=February 9, 2000|last=Kuhnash|first=Jeremy|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2011-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723232645/http://linux.omnipotent.net/article.php?article_id=6937|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1998年發行的''{{tsl|en|Inner Worlds|}}''無論是開發平台還是目標平台都是Linux。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sleepless.com/iw/article.html|title=Internet Based Software Development|publisher=Sleepless Software Inc|date=September 19, 2001|last=Hitchens|first=Joe|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20011231003158/http://sleepless.com/iw/article.html|archivedate=2001年12月31日|accessdate=2016年2月27日}}</ref>1998年，[[Origin_Systems|Origin]]的兩名程式設計師把《[[網路創世紀|網路創世紀]]》移植到Linux。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://reverser.hut.ru/old/linux.htm|title=Ultima Online for Linux|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040229150312/http://reverser.hut.ru/old/linux.htm|archivedate=2004-02-29|accessdate=2016-02-27}}</ref>

[[File:Ryan-Gordon-SELF-2009.png|thumb]]

1998年11月9日，一家名為[[Loki_Software|Loki Software]]的新公司由[[Scott_Draeker|Scott Draeker]]成立，他原本是一名專職軟體授權的律師，因工作接觸到Linux而逐漸有了移植遊戲到Linux上的想法。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/3521|title=Interview: Scott Draeker and Sam Latinga, Loki Entertainment|work={{tsl|en|Linux Journal|}}|date=August 1, 1999|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110231035/https://www.linuxjournal.com/article/3521|dead-url=no}}</ref>Loki雖然在商業上是失敗的，但通常被認為是現代Linux遊戲產業的鼻祖。Loki開發了數款免費的軟體工具，例如Loki installer（又名Loki Setup）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macologist.org/viewtopic.php?t=607|title=Interview with Ryan Gordon: Postal2, Unreal & Mac Gaming – Macologist|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050309061407/http://www.macologist.org/viewtopic.php?t=607|archivedate=2005-03-09|accessdate=2017-11-11}}</ref>，並且支援了[[SDL|SDL]]的開發，以及開始 [[OpenAL|OpenAL]] 音頻庫專案。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/4400|title=The Story of OpenAL|publisher={{tsl|en|Linux Journal|}}|date=January 1, 2001|last=Kreimeier|first=Bernd|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2017-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213160409/https://www.linuxjournal.com/article/4400|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Loki and the Linux World Expo – GameSpy chats with Linux legend Scott Draeker about the future of Linux gaming |url=http://archive.gamespy.com/legacy/articles/loki_a.shtm |last=Hills |first=James |publisher=GameSpy |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060315020137/http://archive.gamespy.com/legacy/articles/loki_a.shtm |archivedate=2006-03-15 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2016-02-27 }}</ref>至今仍被視為Linux遊戲發展的基石。<ref>[http://www.itworld.com/article/2785732/open-source-tools/does-ragnarok-for-loki-spell-doom-for-linux-games-.html Does Ragnarok for Loki Spell Doom for Linux Games?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.itworld.com/article/2785732/open-source-tools/does-ragnarok-for-loki-spell-doom-for-linux-games-.html |date=20180829175620 }}, [[IT_World|IT World]], February 28, 2002 (Article by Eric Foster-Johnson)]</ref>在2002年關閉以前，他們移植了19款知名遊戲。Loki最初時的成功也吸引了其他公司投資Linux遊戲市場，例如{{tsl|en|Tribsoft|}}、{{tsl|en|Hyperion Entertainment|}}、[[Macmillan_Digital_Publishing_USA|Macmillan Digital Publishing USA]]、[[Gray_Matter_Interactive|Xatrix Entertainment]] {{tsl|en|Philos Laboratories|}}和[[Vicarious_Visions|Vicarious Visions]]。這段時期，{{tsl|en|Michael Simms|}}創立了{{tsl|en|Tux Games|}}，這是最早的Linux遊戲線上零售商之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.linuxgamepublishing.com/2009/05/15/lgp-history-pt-1-how-lgp-came-to-be/|title=Linux Game Publishing Blog, LGP History pt 1: How LGP came to be|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713212344/http://blog.linuxgamepublishing.com/2009/05/15/lgp-history-pt-1-how-lgp-came-to-be/|archivedate=2011-07-13|accessdate=2016-02-27}}</ref>

在Loki關閉以後，Linux的遊戲市場開始面臨一些轉變。雖然一些新的公司，例如{{tsl|en|Linux Game Publishing|}}和{{tsl|en|RuneSoft|}}，持續地移植遊戲，但是Linux遊戲的支持者開始鼓勵開發者自行移植遊戲，或是透過個人承包者移植。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=ODkwOA|title=Alternative Games Is All About Linux Gaming|publisher=[[Phoronix|Phoronix]]|date=December 14, 2010|author1={{tsl|en|Michael Larabel|}}|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025081730/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=ODkwOA|dead-url=no}}</ref>一名前Loki的員工{{tsl|en|Ryan C. Gordon|}}即受此影響，在往後十年，他繼續移植遊戲到各個平台上，包含Linux。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardware.no/artikler/ryan_c_gordon_and_michael_simms/68450/2|title=Porting games to Linux|publisher=hardware.no|date=2009-03-10|last=Heggelund Hansen|first=Robin|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2014-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322083056/http://www.hardware.no/artikler/ryan_c_gordon_and_michael_simms/68450/2|dead-url=no}}</ref>這段時間，由id Software開始，許多公司釋出了他們老遊戲的[[原始碼|原始碼]]，老遊戲的{{tsl|en|Source port|}}於是一下子增加了不少，讓Linux在內的系統可以執行這些遊戲。這也幫助許多自由開源遊戲的發展，尤其是[[第一人稱射擊遊戲|第一人稱射擊遊戲]]。<ref name="ljquake3">{{cite web | url = http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/9867 | title = Quake, Meet GPL; GPL, Meet Quake | date = 2007-12-01 | accessdate = 2012-01-12 | publisher = {{tsl|en|Linux Journal|}} | archive-date = 2020-10-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201001060130/https://www.linuxjournal.com/article/9867 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 2010年代 ===

{{Imageframe|width=250|content=[[File:Humblebundlebycount.png|250px]]<br/>[[File:Humblebundlebydonation.png|250px]]|caption=第一個[[Humble_Bundle|Humble Indie Bundle]]在不同平台的銷售量分析，上圖為購買者數量，下圖為付款金額量。藍色為Microsoft Windows，黃色為OS X，紅色為Linux。|align=right}}
在2010前後，Linux遊戲市場開始受到{{link-en|獨立電子遊戲開發|independent video game development}}的崛起衝擊，許多獨立開發者支援多個平台，<ref name="OSNews.com">{{cite web | url = http://www.osnews.com/story/25328/The_State_of_Linux_Gaming_2011 | title = The State of Linux Gaming 2011 | date = 2011-11-14 | accessdate = 2012-01-12 | publisher = OSNews.com | archive-date = 2018-12-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181209145600/http://www.osnews.com/story/25328/The_State_of_Linux_Gaming_2011 | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[Humble_Bundle|Humble Indie Bundle]]讓這個潮流正式的顯現出來，Linux使用者在他們的銷售中佔了可觀的比例，Linux使用者在消費時時常也是最慷慨的。<ref name="humble gdc">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/33272/GDC_2011_Humble_Indie_Bundle_Creators_Talk_Inspiration_Execution.php | title = GDC 2011: Humble Indie Bundle Creators Talk Inspiration, Execution | first = Kyle | last = Orland | date = 2011-02-28 | accessdate = 2011-02-28 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-date = 2012-08-25 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6AAxZ5pJ2?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/33272/GDC_2011_Humble_Indie_Bundle_Creators_Talk_Inspiration_Execution.php | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="humblemoney">{{cite web | url = http://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2011/12/linux-users-continue-to-most-for-the-humble-indie-bundle/ | title = Linux Users Continue To Pay Most for the @Humble Indie Bundle | first = Joey | last = Sneddon | date = 2011-12-21 | accessdate = 2012-01-12 | publisher = {{tsl|de|OMG! Ubuntu!|}} | archive-date = 2019-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190526163417/https://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2011/12/linux-users-continue-to-most-for-the-humble-indie-bundle | dead-url = no }}</ref>一些評論者也認為，Linux版的{{tsl|en|Desura|}}，一個主要注重於小型獨立開發者的[[數位發行|數位發行]]平台， 諭示了市場終於把Linux作為遊戲平台的一大步。<ref name="OSNews.com" /><ref name="cheese">{{cite web | url = http://www.twolofbees.com/cheesetalks/desura.php | title = cheese talks to himself – Desura Beta | date = 2011-10-11 | accessdate = 2011-11-07 | publisher = twolofbees.com | archive-date = 2011-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111213020838/http://twolofbees.com/cheesetalks/desura.php | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="arstechnica2015">{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/02/the-state-of-linux-gaming-in-the-steamos-era/1/ | title = The state of Linux gaming in the SteamOS era | date = 2015-02-26 | accessdate = 2015-02-27 | publisher = [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] | archive-date = 2016-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160119165933/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/02/the-state-of-linux-gaming-in-the-steamos-era/1/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 在2009年，一家獨立遊戲小公司Entourev LLC發行了Voltley，這是Linux上最早的商業獨占遊戲。同年，LGP發行Shadowgrounds，第1款使用Nvidia PhysX中間軟體的商業Linux遊戲。

[[File:Gabe_Newell_GDC_2010.jpg|thumb]]稱「Linux和開源是遊戲的未來」。<ref name="arstechnicaGabeNewell">{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/09/gabe-newell-linux-is-the-future-of-gaming-new-hardware-coming-soon/ | title = Gabe Newell: Linux is the future of gaming, new hardware coming soon | date = 2013-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-02-27 | publisher = [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] | archive-date = 2017-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171201203353/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/09/gabe-newell-linux-is-the-future-of-gaming-new-hardware-coming-soon/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>]]

2012年7月，遊戲開發和發行商[[維爾福|維爾福]]發佈Linux版的[[Source引擎|Source引擎]]，並宣佈他們要把數位發行平台[[Steam|Steam]]帶到Linux上。<ref>{{cite web |last=Albanesius |first=Chloe |url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2407237,00.asp |title=Valve Moves Forward With Steam for Linux | News & Opinion |publisher=PCMag.com |date=2012-07-17 |accessdate=2014-03-18 |archive-date=2017-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171021075224/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2407237,00.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://blogs.valvesoftware.com/linux/steamd-penguins/ | title = Steam’d Penguins | publisher = [[Valve_Corporation|Valve Corporation]] | date = 2012-07-16 | accessdate = 2012-07-16 | archive-date = 2013-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130812085002/http://blogs.valvesoftware.com/linux/steamd-penguins/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.theverge.com/gaming/2012/7/16/3163717/left-4-dead-2-to-be-first-valve-game-on-linux | title = 'Left 4 Dead 2' to be first Valve game on Linux | first = Tracey | last = Lein | date = 2012-07-16 | accessdate = 2012-07-16 | publisher = [[The_Verve|The Verve]] | archive-date = 2012-10-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121001182932/http://www.theverge.com/gaming/2012/7/16/3163717/left-4-dead-2-to-be-first-valve-game-on-linux | dead-url = no }}</ref>Linux版的Steam客戶端讓其他開發者開始考慮移植遊戲到Linux上，<ref name="arstechnica2015" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2012/07/25/serious-sam-3-bfe-headed-to-steam-ubuntu/ | title = Serious Sam 3: BFE headed to Steam Ubuntu | first = Brenna | last = Hillier | date = 2012-07-24 | accessdate = 2012-07-24 | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-date = 2020-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200310035856/https://www.vg247.com/2012/07/25/serious-sam-3-bfe-headed-to-steam-ubuntu/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=ODI4NA | title = Valve's Linux Play May Lead More Games To Follow